author: By Alicia Lee, CNN
title: Easter Bunny named Jacinda flies as sole passenger on flight to collect stranded Germans in New Zealand
description: Despite the rest of us being stuck at home Sunday, the Easter Bunny is still working hard to bring joy to people around the world. And for one Easter Bunny named Jacinda, that means flying across the world to bring stranded travelers back home.
content:
